dcterms:description: A large scale dataset containing LiDAR data at the packet level, along with accurate ego-pose and associated object bounding box annotations at the same temporal resolution (i.e., 100Hz). It includes 6500 snippets with diverse conditions (e.g., geographical, lighting, road topology, vehicle types) and a total of 16,250,000 packets (1,625,000 frames).
dcterms:title: PACKETATG4D
